1
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:23,920
Master Wang,

2
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:26,559
the Young Master seems
to have vanished without a trace.

3
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:29,519
We haven't found a single clue.

4
00:00:29,559 --> 00:00:30,160
Useless fools!

5
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,320
What about Laifu?

6
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:34,640
The men we sent after him

7
00:00:34,759 --> 00:00:36,479
have disappeared, too.

8
00:00:36,679 --> 00:00:38,039
You...

9
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:39,399
Master Wang,

10
00:00:39,399 --> 00:00:40,359
please rest assured.

11
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:41,799
I inquired at the Bureau.

12
00:00:42,066 --> 00:00:43,200
They never caught him either.

13
00:00:43,288 --> 00:00:44,780
They are posting notices on the streets.

14
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:46,560
Go find him!

15
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,159
Ten thousand in silver
for whoever finds him!

16
00:00:48,159 --> 00:00:49,640
Ten thousand for catching Laifu?

17
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:51,911
For finding the Young Master!
The Young Master!

18
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:53,399
You senseless fool!

19
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:56,000
Get out!

20
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:57,719
Ten thousand...

21
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,840
Wang Dingrong really loves his son.

22
00:01:01,479 --> 00:01:03,960
Hengshun Salt Bureau is now
in complete chaos.

23
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,920
Wang Dingrong has
even fallen ill because of it.

24
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,200
It seems he has gone missing, then.

25
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:12,640
(Missing or in hiding)

26
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,840
I've found the physician

27
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,519
who treated
Wang Dingrong's leg back then.

28
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:18,040
Wang Dingrong claimed
his leg was broken from a fall.

29
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,959
But when the physician examined it...

30
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:25,040
Master Wang's leg

31
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,840
wasn't broken from a fall.

32
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,560
Someone

33
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,680
broke his leg.

34
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:33,400
If he was beaten,
why claim it was a fall?

35
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,400
Could he be hiding something?

36
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,799
The sinking of the Qi family's ship

37
00:01:39,359 --> 00:01:41,480
is looking more and more
like premeditated foul play.

38
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,159
With Wang Xian missing,

39
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,920
the letter written to Laifu...

40
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,640
Who exactly wrote it?

41
00:01:55,060 --> 00:02:01,300
=The Tang Mist S1=

42
00:03:19,820 --> 00:03:22,020
=Episode 5=

43
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,439
This dirty old man sure is fast.

44
00:03:31,533 --> 00:03:33,960
Ledgers and water transport dispatches
from the Wang family's

45
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:36,840
first and most recent six months
managing the salt bureau.

46
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,159
And these are from the Qi family's

47
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,759
last six months, and two years ago.

48
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,680
Lin, why don't you come over and help?

49
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,120
Let's look into this together.

50
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,439
Because he

51
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:48,840
can not read.

52
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:53,980
(Signatory: Wang Xian)

53
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:57,039
Since Wang Dingrong is in charge,

54
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,560
why are the signatories
on all the accounts

55
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,960
Wang Xian?

56
00:04:04,039 --> 00:04:04,840
Wang Xian.

57
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,240
Wang Xian.

58
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,400
Wang Xian.

59
00:04:10,644 --> 00:04:12,120
It really is him on all of them.

60
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:19,240
Why is there no record

61
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,600
of the Qi family's shipwreck?

62
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,720
Furthermore,
after the Wang family took over,

63
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,759
this batch of official salt

64
00:04:23,759 --> 00:04:25,160
was never dispatched again.

65
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,879
It is a significant loss, after all.

66
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,680
I guess Wang Dingrong was unwilling

67
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,480
to take it on.

68
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:38,333
(Water Transport Dispatch.
Cargo: Liu Shun.)

69
00:04:38,355 --> 00:04:39,740
(Come to Hengshun Salt Bureau
at night for the money.)

70
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,519
(Shun)

71
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:44,240
There is no need to investigate
the shipwreck case anymore.

72
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,040
Since

73
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:50,240
our goal is the same
as the water ghost's,

74
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:52,800
we just wait to uncover
the water ghost's true face,

75
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,040
and the truth will
naturally be revealed.

76
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,000
Master,

77
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,839
you seem to have missed something.

78
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,959
This water ghost, Qi Feng,

79
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,759
is already dead.

80
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:11,920
Carefully compare
these three "Shun" characters.

81
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,044
The "Shun" on the note Laifu received,

82
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:21,822
the "Shun" of Hengshun Salt Bureau,

83
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,755
and the "Shun"
in Liu Shun's death dispatch...

84
00:05:23,777 --> 00:05:24,630
are exactly the same.

85
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,839
Moreover, the handwriting on the note

86
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:27,920
is not Wang Xian's.

87
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,920
It was written
by the water ghost to Laifu.

88
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,959
The water ghost

89
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,120
is not Qi Feng.

90
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:46,360
(What exactly have we overlooked?)

91
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,839
(Where exactly does the problem lie?)

92
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:56,160
(The thumb ring.)

93
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,600
(The note.)

94
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,920
(Since you knew
how to impersonate Wang Xian)

95
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,480
(to lure Laifu out,)

96
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:07,839
(you must be intimately
familiar with all of this.)

97
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,759
(You lured Laifu out)

98
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:13,079
(and allowed the Bureau
to capture him easily.)

99
00:06:13,079 --> 00:06:14,600
(Your goal)

100
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,800
(was to have Laifu
testify against Wang Xian.)

101
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,480
It belongs to Wang Xian.

102
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,560
(You did it to prove that)

103
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,560
(Wang Xian murdered to silence them.)

104
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:25,360
(You must hate Wang Xian to the bone.)

105
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:28,279
(Who exactly are you?)

106
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,839
In order to give my daughter

107
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:38,839
a place to express her grief...

108
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,199
Such devotion

109
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,399
is rare and precious.

110
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,639
Commissioner Di,

111
00:06:47,399 --> 00:06:49,040
my daughter's mind has not recovered.

112
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:50,399
She cannot withstand any shock.

113
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,319
Please...

114
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,600
Rest assured.

115
00:06:54,439 --> 00:06:55,240
I understand.

116
00:06:57,879 --> 00:06:58,639
Ruo.

117
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,160
Commissioner Di.

118
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,040
We have captured Laifu.

119
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:12,839
He fully confessed
to Wang Xian's crimes.

120
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:14,839
And he testified that Wang Xian

121
00:07:14,839 --> 00:07:16,439
murdered Cai to silence him.

122
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:18,199
Hence,

123
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,360
we can finally give Lady Du

124
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,360
an explanation

125
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,800
regarding Qi Feng's death.

126
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,639
Lady Du,

127
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:32,439
aren't you concerned
about Wang Xian's whereabouts?

128
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,480
With you here,

129
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:38,040
Wang Xian will surely be caught.

130
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:39,920
Commissioner Di,

131
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:42,480
what about the sinking
of the Qi family's ship?

132
00:07:44,959 --> 00:07:46,680
This case is already two years old.

133
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,800
Evidence is nowhere to be found.

134
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,839
Please forgive me, Lady Du.

135
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:54,279
The Wang family scuttled the ship.

136
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:59,199
Where did you learn this?

137
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:00,600
Half a year ago,

138
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:03,040
Wang Xian said so himself.

139
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,660
(Wedding)

140
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,439
Qi Feng,

141
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:17,177
even though
we were not formally married,

142
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,680
in my heart,

143
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:23,000
you are the only husband I'll ever have.

144
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:26,199
You have been gone for so long.

145
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,680
It is time for you to come back.

146
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,360
He's never coming back.

147
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,822
What are you doing here?

148
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,320
If I hadn't followed you...

149
00:08:43,311 --> 00:08:45,600
I never would've known
about this nice little spot.

150
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,759
Qi Feng is dead.

151
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,639
He died in the river.

152
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:52,720
He's never coming back.

153
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:53,720
Shut up!

154
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,000
Listen up!

155
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,799
Qi Feng isn't coming back!

156
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,480
I had his ship scuttled.

157
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,639
I killed him.

158
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,039
Do you know why?

159
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,720
Because I love you,

160
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,519
Ruo.

161
00:09:08,799 --> 00:09:10,519
But why do you only have eyes for him?

162
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,320
We were childhood friends too.

163
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,600
We grew up together too!

164
00:09:13,639 --> 00:09:14,840
Why does he get to have you,

165
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,080
while I could only watch?

166
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,080
Let go of me!

167
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,155
Because he's
the Young Master of the salt bureau,

168
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:23,279
and I'm just a poor boy?

169
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:27,799
It doesn't matter.

170
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,399
For you, I can

171
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:31,879
take everything from him.

172
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:34,120
And destroy it all.

173
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:35,440
Despicable!

174
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,480
I'm going to report you!

175
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,720
I'll report you to the Bureau!

176
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,080
Ruo.

177
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,960
You're a smart girl.

178
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:41,759
Surely you realize

179
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:43,639
that I could take over
Hengshun so easily.

180
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,600
I'm not afraid of you reporting me.

181
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,759
One time,

182
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,080
you fell into my arms.

183
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,559
Ever since then,

184
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,399
you're all I dream about.

185
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,840
Let me go!

186
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:04,080
You two used to secretly meet here.

187
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:06,399
Now, it's ours.

188
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:32,266
I wanted to report it to the Bureau.

189
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,320
But I didn't have any evidence.

190
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,639
And I couldn't put my father in danger.

191
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:48,960
Commissioner Di,

192
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:51,000
my daughter needs to rest.

193
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,120
Please leave.

194
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,039
Did Wang Xian

195
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,879
also find out

196
00:10:57,879 --> 00:11:00,159
that Qi Feng is the water ghost?

197
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,759
He didn't.

198
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,159
It's all my fault.

199
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,039
I was careless.

200
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:10,600
I accidentally exposed the letter.

201
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:14,039
It brought death upon Qi Feng.

202
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:17,159
I hate myself.

203
00:11:18,399 --> 00:11:19,720
I just watched helplessly

204
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:21,720
as he burned in the fire.

205
00:11:24,480 --> 00:11:25,639
Commissioner Di,

206
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,519
we've told you

207
00:11:26,559 --> 00:11:28,840
everything we should
and shouldn't about the Wang family.

208
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,759
My daughter really
can't take any more shock.

209
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,759
Please.

210
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:56,480
What was Qi Feng's shoe size?

211
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,240
Why do you ask?

212
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:06,080
Nothing important.

213
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,080
Could you tell me?

214
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,559
Qi Feng is dead.

215
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:14,799
I couldn't tell you.

216
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,159
Before you started the fire,

217
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,720
did you look inside the room?

218
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,320
What state was the victim in?

219
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,039
He was

220
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,080
lying on the bed.

221
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,519
Did you see his face?

222
00:12:42,919 --> 00:12:44,440
His back was to the window.

223
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,720
I didn't notice.

224
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:47,240
Before you killed someone,

225
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,960
didn't you even verify their identity?

226
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,440
Commissioner Di,

227
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,960
it was our first time
doing something like this.

228
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:56,679
We were too panicked at the time.

229
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,720
The fire in that room

230
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:59,279
shot up so high all of a sudden.

231
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,559
I was too scared.

232
00:13:01,559 --> 00:13:03,000
I didn't dare look.

233
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,919
The fire in the room?

234
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:06,919
Think again.

235
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,844
Is there anything else you left out?

236
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:12,679
The fire

237
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:14,360
even burned onto him.

238
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,279
He seemed not to have

239
00:13:16,399 --> 00:13:17,200
moved at all

240
00:13:17,759 --> 00:13:19,279
right from the start.

241
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,639
He never moved?

242
00:13:37,399 --> 00:13:38,600
(Laifu said)

243
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:41,360
(that a huge fire broke out
in the room instantly.)

244
00:13:49,639 --> 00:13:51,000
It's flint.

245
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,960
Just as I thought.

246
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,840
(I thought this fire
looked strange at first glance.)

247
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:05,600
(The night the fire started,
there was a southeast wind.)

248
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,720
(The flames rushed southeast.)

249
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:09,879
(Therefore, the wood there)

250
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:12,240
(should be the place
that burned the fiercest.)

251
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:14,480
(The scorched wood
should be grayish-white.)

252
00:14:17,039 --> 00:14:19,440
(Why is it that burnt wood
around the bed)

253
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:20,879
(also grayish-white?)

254
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,960
(So the root cause was here.)

255
00:14:33,039 --> 00:14:33,799
Light it up.

256
00:14:36,039 --> 00:14:36,960
You do it.

257
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,679
(Du Ruo claimed)

258
00:14:49,679 --> 00:14:50,559
Qi Feng!

259
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:53,200
(she witnessed Qi Feng
struggling in the fire,)

260
00:14:53,519 --> 00:14:56,240
(- but was hit by a beam when escaping.)
- Ruo!

261
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,840
Qi Feng!

262
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:06,960
(But Laifu said)

263
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:09,240
(the burning man didn't move at all.)

264
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,960
(Who's lying?)

265
00:15:14,279 --> 00:15:15,279
(Or...)

266
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,759
(Are neither of them lying?)

267
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,240
Master!

268
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,399
Bad news!

269
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,039
Did you find Xian?

270
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,720
No. It's not about the Young Master.

271
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,080
It's Qi Feng.

272
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:49,879
Qi Feng?

273
00:15:50,399 --> 00:15:51,600
Qi Feng is the water ghost.

274
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:53,360
He killed Sun Qi and the other two.

275
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:54,320
And he also knows

276
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,200
that the Young Master
had his ship scuttled.

277
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:58,240
Even Di Renjie and his people know now.

278
00:15:58,519 --> 00:16:00,399
What proof does he have
that it was my son?

279
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,519
The Young Master was drunk.

280
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:04,000
He told Lady Du Ruo

281
00:16:04,039 --> 00:16:04,759
everything he did!

282
00:16:04,759 --> 00:16:06,600
If Di Renjie wants to find evidence,

283
00:16:06,639 --> 00:16:08,320
it'll only take him the blink of an eye.

284
00:16:08,519 --> 00:16:09,720
You have to think of something!

285
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:11,200
The most important thing now

286
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,120
is saving the Young Master's life!

287
00:16:13,200 --> 00:16:14,120
Think of something?

288
00:16:14,159 --> 00:16:16,120
What else can I possibly do?

289
00:16:16,120 --> 00:16:17,039
Then...

290
00:16:18,039 --> 00:16:18,960
This...

291
00:16:20,777 --> 00:16:22,177
The prefectural office...

292
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:22,919
Right.

293
00:16:22,919 --> 00:16:24,000
Go to the prefectural office.

294
00:16:24,010 --> 00:16:26,399
(Ruanjiang County Bureau)

295
00:16:26,399 --> 00:16:27,879
These are Qi Feng's bills,

296
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:30,519
along with the dispatches and letters

297
00:16:30,759 --> 00:16:31,720
he personally signed.

298
00:16:33,060 --> 00:16:35,900
(Qi Feng)

299
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:38,519
Du Ruo brought us Qi Feng's corpse,

300
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:40,879
yet I completely overlooked

301
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,919
the authenticity of Qi Feng's letter.

302
00:16:43,639 --> 00:16:44,840
Who wrote that letter?

303
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:50,519
It was Du Ruo.

304
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:53,200
She's skilled
in calligraphy and painting.

305
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,840
Forging this handwriting

306
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,519
would've been effortless for her.

307
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,519
Without a careful comparison,

308
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:02,279
it's incredibly hard
to spot the difference.

309
00:17:02,279 --> 00:17:05,500
(Ship)

310
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:15,780
(Ruanjiang County Bureau)

311
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:24,000
Please announce me.

312
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,000
Du Ruo is here to take her husband home.

313
00:17:27,759 --> 00:17:29,480
Why would she forge the letters?

314
00:17:30,519 --> 00:17:32,000
We let the shipwreck

315
00:17:32,039 --> 00:17:33,039
cloud our judgment.

316
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:35,359
If we had just believed from the start

317
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:37,400
that Wang Xian really went missing...

318
00:17:42,519 --> 00:17:43,480
The answer

319
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,960
lies with that charred corpse.

320
00:17:48,119 --> 00:17:48,960
Lady Du,

321
00:17:49,799 --> 00:17:50,839
what brings you here?

322
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,519
Official,

323
00:17:52,519 --> 00:17:53,680
the killer has been caught,

324
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:55,200
and Qi Feng's case is solved.

325
00:17:55,599 --> 00:17:56,720
I'm here to take him home.

326
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:04,839
Where's Du Ruo?

327
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:05,799
She left.

328
00:18:05,799 --> 00:18:06,759
What about the corpse?

329
00:18:13,119 --> 00:18:13,759
It's right here.

330
00:18:15,079 --> 00:18:16,119
That was close.

331
00:18:17,066 --> 00:18:18,240
The case isn't fully closed.

332
00:18:18,279 --> 00:18:20,000
I'd never
let anything happen to the body.

333
00:18:20,839 --> 00:18:21,359
Qinglan,

334
00:18:21,519 --> 00:18:22,640
do another autopsy.

335
00:18:32,799 --> 00:18:33,559
Magistrate Cao.

336
00:18:40,759 --> 00:18:41,640
Sir,

337
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,440
look here.

338
00:18:46,759 --> 00:18:48,880
A massive amount of soot
in his windpipe and lungs.

339
00:18:49,279 --> 00:18:51,160
His lungs are a purplish-black.

340
00:19:06,839 --> 00:19:08,559
It seems there are traces of drugs.

341
00:19:09,799 --> 00:19:12,000
He must have
lost consciousness from the drugs

342
00:19:12,319 --> 00:19:14,200
and unknowingly inhaled all that soot.

343
00:19:16,440 --> 00:19:17,440
That makes sense.

344
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,960
I was careless.

345
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:38,000
Judging by his bone structure,

346
00:19:39,079 --> 00:19:39,880
it's a perfect match.

347
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,759
This is Wang Xian?

348
00:19:50,359 --> 00:19:51,200
Then where is Qi Feng?

349
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,480
There is no Qi Feng.

350
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:04,666
(Preview of Next Episode)

351
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:05,839
I'm sorry.

352
00:20:05,839 --> 00:20:07,400
I...

353
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,680
I didn't mean to.

354
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,039
Ruo,

355
00:20:11,400 --> 00:20:12,880
I couldn't help myself.

356
00:20:15,279 --> 00:20:16,759
Forget about him.

357
00:20:16,759 --> 00:20:18,240
Start over with me.

358
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:19,960
Let's start over.

359
00:20:30,470 --> 00:20:32,050
♪Night covers the long streets♪

360
00:20:33,130 --> 00:20:34,840
♪The city remains silent♪

361
00:20:36,230 --> 00:20:37,820
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

362
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:40,320
♪Words still left unspoken♪

363
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:43,360
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

364
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,960
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

365
00:20:47,580 --> 00:20:49,060
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

366
00:20:49,060 --> 00:20:52,200
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

367
00:20:52,820 --> 00:20:54,740
♪Love is born from desire♪

368
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:57,560
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

369
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:00,360
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

370
00:21:00,360 --> 00:21:03,660
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

371
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,430
♪Someone once warned me♪

372
00:21:06,430 --> 00:21:07,950
♪To stop upon this shore♪

373
00:21:07,950 --> 00:21:09,270
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

374
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:10,760
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

375
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:11,880
♪If one thought retreats♪

376
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,180
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

377
00:21:13,180 --> 00:21:14,520
♪But in this world♪

378
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:16,920
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

379
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:21,560
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

380
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:23,030
♪Still I walk ahead♪

381
00:21:23,260 --> 00:21:24,480
♪Let it pierce through♪

382
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:29,220
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

383
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:31,460
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

384
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,860
♪Covering every heart♪

385
00:21:32,860 --> 00:21:34,050
♪How many people♪

386
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:35,680
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

387
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:37,890
♪Yet call it♪

388
00:21:38,090 --> 00:21:39,430
♪Fate?♪

389
00:21:39,790 --> 00:21:40,970
♪Life and death♪

390
00:21:40,970 --> 00:21:42,230
♪Balanced on a single line♪

391
00:21:42,580 --> 00:21:43,750
♪Light and shadow♪

392
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:45,010
♪Hanging side by side♪

393
00:21:45,010 --> 00:21:46,490
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

394
00:21:46,490 --> 00:21:47,900
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

395
00:21:47,900 --> 00:21:49,440
♪In the end, it is only♪

396
00:21:49,440 --> 00:21:50,820
♪A single misguided thought♪

397
00:21:50,820 --> 00:21:52,380
♪If unveiling the truth♪

398
00:21:52,380 --> 00:21:53,720
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

399
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,890
♪Then this answer♪

400
00:21:54,890 --> 00:21:56,250
♪Can it still remain true?♪

401
00:21:56,250 --> 00:21:57,650
♪When love and law♪

402
00:21:57,650 --> 00:21:59,130
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

403
00:21:59,130 --> 00:22:00,530
♪Which figure before me♪

404
00:22:00,530 --> 00:22:07,730
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

405
00:22:07,730 --> 00:22:10,460
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

406
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:12,050
♪Still I walk ahead♪

407
00:22:12,050 --> 00:22:13,290
♪Not for fame or glory♪

408
00:22:13,290 --> 00:22:18,160
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

409
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:19,970
♪Human nature is clouded♪

410
00:22:19,970 --> 00:22:21,690
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

411
00:22:21,690 --> 00:22:23,160
♪Though this world♪

412
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,530
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

413
00:22:24,530 --> 00:22:26,780
♪There is still a light♪

414
00:22:26,780 --> 00:22:29,740
♪Worth pursuing♪

415
00:22:29,740 --> 00:22:31,560
♪Every case has its ending♪

416
00:22:31,560 --> 00:22:32,820
♪But night does not always fade♪

417
00:22:33,090 --> 00:22:34,470
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

418
00:22:34,470 --> 00:22:35,690
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

419
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,040
♪If justice stands♪

420
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:38,290
♪Without mercy beside it♪

421
00:22:38,290 --> 00:22:40,090
♪Then how is it♪

422
00:22:40,090 --> 00:22:49,650
♪Any different from a blade?♪

423
00:22:49,650 --> 00:22:52,840
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

424
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:54,320
♪Still I walk ahead♪

425
00:22:54,320 --> 00:22:55,710
♪Even if the world♪

426
00:22:55,710 --> 00:23:00,440
♪Refuses to answer♪

427
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:02,400
♪When every hidden truth♪

428
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:04,110
♪Finally reveals itself♪

429
00:23:04,110 --> 00:23:05,470
♪I only wish♪

430
00:23:05,470 --> 00:23:06,950
♪To hold on♪

431
00:23:06,950 --> 00:23:11,690
♪Within the darkness♪

432
00:23:11,690 --> 00:23:13,690
♪To the heart♪

